languages.text: "Ну и лицемерный же ты ашмаг, шестеренка". {n}Поймав гневный взгляд Паскаля, Джай широко ухмыляется.{/n} "Давай, скажи еще разок, что это я тяну руки к тому, чего нельзя касаться".

"What a hypocritical ashmag you are, cog." {n}Jae meets Pasqal's glare and smirks.{/n} "Go ahead, look me in the eye and tell me again that I'm the one who wants to get my hands on things no one should ever touch."

languages.text: 「なんて偽善的なクソ野郎なの」{n}ジェイはパスカルの睨みを受け、にやりと笑った。{/n}「さあ、もう一度あたしの目を見て、触れてはいけないものに手を出したいと思っているその対象は、本当にあたしだって言ってごらん」

languages.text: « Vous êtes vraiment un ashmag hypocrite, le boulon. {n}Jae croise le regard furieux de Pasqal et lui adresse un sourire provocateur.{/n} Allez-y, regardez-moi droit dans les yeux et redites-moi que je suis celle qui veut s'emparer de choses que personne ne devrait jamais toucher. »

languages.text: “你可真是个虚伪的坏种，齿轮人。”{n}婕伊直视着帕斯卡的目光，冷笑起来。{/n}“你总是说我打算染指那些任何人都不该染指的东西，可看看你现在的样子。你敢看着我的眼睛，再重复一遍你之前的话吗？”

languages.text: «Menudo ashmag hipócrita está hecho, don Engranajes». {n}Jae y Pasqal cruzan miradas y esta sonríe.{/n} «Venga, míreme a los ojos y vuelva a decir que soy la única que quiere poner las zarpas en lo que nadie debería tocar».
languages.original_text: "What a hypocritical ashmag you are, cog." {n}Jae meets Pasqal's glare and smirks.{/n} "Go ahead, look me in the eye and tell me again that I'm the one who wants to get my hands on things no one should ever touch."

languages.text: "Was seid Ihr doch für ein heuchlerischer Ashmag, Cog." {n}Jae blickt den zornigen Pasqal ruhig an und grinst.{/n} "Nun seht mir in die Augen und sagt mir noch einmal, dass ich es bin, die an Dingen interessier ist, die niemand jemals anrühren sollte."
languages.original_text: "What a hypocritical ashmag you are, cog." {n}Jae meets Pasqal's glare and smirks.{/n} "Go ahead, look me in the eye and tell me again that I'm the one who wants to get my hands on things no one should ever touch."

languages.text: "Dişli, sen var ya ikiyüzlü külboğazın tekisin" {n}Jae, dik dik bakan Pasqal'la göz göze gelip sırıtıyor.{/n} "Hadi, gözümün içine bak... Kimsenin el uzatmaması gereken şeyleri kendime saklamamam gerektiğini söyle bana."
languages.original_text: "What a hypocritical ashmag you are, cog." {n}Jae meets Pasqal's glare and smirks.{/n} "Go ahead, look me in the eye and tell me again that I'm the one who wants to get my hands on things no one should ever touch."

traits.locale_text: "İkiyüzlü külboğazın tekisin, seni dişli." {n}Dik dik bakan Pasqal'la göz göze gelen Jae sırıtıyor.{/n} "Hadi, gözümün içine bak… Kimsenin el uzatmaması gereken şeyleri kendime saklamamam gerektiğini söyle bana."
